Title: Fresh Bones
Plot: While investigating several deaths and murders within a Haitian refugee camp, Mulder and Scully get caught in the middle of a secret war between the camp commander and a Voodoo priest.
GuestStars: Kevin Conway, Katya Gardener, Roger R. Cross, Peter Kelamis, Adrien Malebranche, Bruce A. Young, Daniel Benzali, Jamil Walker Smith, Callum Keith Rennie, Matt Hill
